The Milliard Gargantubrain was a super-computer from Maximegalon which Lunkwill said had the ability to "count all the atoms in a star in a millisecond."Dialogue from Fit the Fourth from The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy: The Original Radio Scripts, Douglas Adams, 1985 

Deep Thought called it a mere abacus in comparison to itself, and would rather not have it mentioned. Radio series 
